01:03:28,346 --> 01:03:31,933
initials.
L is for "let me have this, please."

716
01:03:32,016 --> 01:03:34,268
H is for "Hae-seok, I'm begging you."

717
01:03:34,352 --> 01:03:36,729
S is for, "Sucks to be us, wouldn't you
say?"

718
01:03:37,230 --> 01:03:38,564
What do you think?

719
01:03:43,736 --> 01:03:45,738
CHANGE PHONE NUMBER

720
01:03:45,822 --> 01:03:46,823
ARE YOU SURE?

721
01:03:46,906 --> 01:03:48,324
YOUR NUMBER HAS BEEN CHANGED

722
01:05:07,570 --> 01:05:08,404
-Who is--
-Mom!

723
01:05:12,158 --> 01:05:12,992
Hello?

724
01:05:13,576 --> 01:05:15,411
Mom, you took forever to answer.

725
01:05:43,105 --> 01:05:45,816
SOLD OUT ON YOU

726
01:05:45,900 --> 01:05:51,864
THANK YOU TO MR. AHN SANG-WOO
FOR HIS SPECIAL APPEARANCE

727
01:06:15,638 --> 01:06:17,765
What a lovely pair! You look wonderful
together!

728
01:06:17,848 --> 01:06:19,725
I'm sorry for the misunderstanding
yesterday.

729
01:06:19,809 --> 01:06:21,477
I understand why it happened. Let's drop
it.

730
01:06:21,560 --> 01:06:22,645
Dam Ye-jin?

731
01:06:22,728 --> 01:06:25,356
Hello. This is, Dam Ye-jin. I'm your
customer service representative.

732
01:06:25,439 --> 01:06:28,150
Is this HIT? How could you get something
this wrong?

733
01:06:28,234 --> 01:06:30,111
-I came because you called me.
-Go away, please!

734
01:06:30,194 --> 01:06:31,320
Let me in!

735
01:06:33,906 --> 01:06:35,116
What is she doing here?

736
01:06:36,200 --> 01:06:38,202
Do you not remember me at all?

737
01:06:38,285 --> 01:06:40,329
Let's settle things with L'Etoile
once and for all.

738
01:06:40,413 --> 01:06:43,666
-Are you sure? We're not just any brand.
-Do you have nothing to say to me?

739
01:06:43,749 --> 01:06:45,584
I hope we never see each other again.

